{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","text":"WCAG21Requirements"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV15requirementsAAASb7textual_Sb10nonTextualtvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"requirementsAAA"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"WCAG 2.1 requirement for AAA level needs to have textual component matching 7:1 contrast ratio"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and non textual component matching 4.5:1 contrast ratio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is recommended for mobiles devices projects (because of screen sizes and luminosity issues)."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/WCAG21Requirements","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"WCAG21Requirements"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/requirementsAAA"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/requirementsaaa"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","title":"the following guidelines","url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"the following guidelines","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio/requirementsAAA":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/requirementsaaa","title":"requirementsAAA","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"WCAG 2.1 requirement for AAA level needs to have textual component matching 7:1 contrast ratio","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and non textual component matching 4.5:1 contrast ratio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is recommended for mobiles devices projects (because of screen sizes and luminosity issues).","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/requirementsAAA","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"WCAG21Requirements"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"title":"Foundations","kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_layers.png"}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations"},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/WCAG21Requirements":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"WCAG 2.1 AA and AAA requirements use ratio for textual and non textual components"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"WCAG21Requirements"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/WCAG21Requirements","title":"WCAG21Requirements","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"WCAG21Requirements","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/wcag21requirements"},"ic_layers.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"ic_layers.png"}}}